{"tid":757387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國歐盟達成貿易協定　中國連歐制美失敗","createTime":"2018-07-26T21:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T23:06:39.000Z","uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e85ff1ecd5eb22fd2da417e7208e75e757e5ca","tid":757387,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:30:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/news-us-eu-trade-and-china-20180726/4500784.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fnews-us-eu-trade-and-china-20180726%2F4500784.html&d=YDpFvmEDpF5LG4WvhAwVkRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=e31951a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/news-us-eu-trade-and-china-20180726/4500784.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國歐盟達成貿易協定 中國連歐制美失敗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/47E713BA-3FD6-4B88-9A8C-89A056962684_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F47E713BA-3FD6-4B88-9A8C-89A056962684_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=c43e4c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國與歐盟達成框架協議，同意在非汽車類產品領域將實現&ldquo;零關稅、零補貼&rdquo;。根據這一協定，歐盟將向美國擴大採購在美中貿易戰中倍受打擊的大豆等產品。<br />\n<br />\n在美中貿易爭端中，中國一直抨擊美國破壞國際經濟秩序，&rdquo; 把美國一個國家的利益淩駕在全球利益之上&rdquo;，希望團結歐盟等其他國家來對抗美國。<br />\n<br />\n川普總統星期三在宣佈美國歐盟貿易大和解之後說，這是自由與公平貿易的大日子。川普總統表示，美國與歐盟的雙邊貿易額達到一兆美元，是全球最大的經濟合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n川普總統還說，歐盟承諾將在最短時間內開始從美國中西部購買大量大豆，與此同時，川普總統在推文中則批中國針對大豆的做法相當&ldquo;惡毒&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n白宮的新聞稿說，美歐貿易協定為美國與歐盟關係開啟新格局，美國和歐盟共計有超過8.3億名公民、占全球GDP的50%以上，美歐合作將讓全球變得更美好、安全和繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人耿爽26日表示，中國也希望美歐有關努力和舉措符合&ldquo;多邊貿易規則，比如非歧視原則等&rdquo; 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果美國和歐盟一旦達成世界上最大的美歐自貿區，這一貿易區將與世界上第二大自貿區日歐自貿區重疊，全球貿易規則和貿易秩序將自然發生根本性改變。有分析人士擔心，令中國幾十年來享盡各種利益的世界貿易組織可能會失去意義，可能是世界貿易組織體制開始瓦解的開始。</span><br />\n<br />\n美歐星期三的聲明中也提到將對世界貿易組織WTO體制進行改革。<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部星期四對此提醒說，希望世貿組織改革&ldquo;反映大多數成員的訴求，通過漸進式的改革&rdquo;，並強調說，改革要&ldquo;確保世貿組織基本宗旨不變，基本原則不受挑戰&rdquo;，還要&ldquo;增強世貿組織的權威性和領導力&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"88689704d1248ba2921bc8ebcf43e902e9476acb","tid":757387,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:40:20.000Z","msg":"Brics back 'open world economy' that benefits all nations <a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-44973352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-44973352&d=YDpFvmEDpF5LG4WvhAwVkRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f71b90a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-44973352</a><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要，習大大有金磚五國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聯合亮劍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e46e8fda25b7d5f72f7c0d0a28aa91c4efbb59d","tid":757387,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619287e9abf590b8d4807a85294f3db382ce73b9","tid":757387,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/l0MYMlC87bFwYKEdG/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl0MYMlC87bFwYKEdG%2Fgiphy.gif&h=cd4f8a61&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}